293
00:26:59,020 --> 00:27:00,240
Let's continue.

294
00:27:06,180 --> 00:27:07,350
Watch your step.

295
00:28:01,180 --> 00:28:02,200
This place

296
00:28:02,850 --> 00:28:04,760
should be the Yinshaluo's shrine

297
00:28:05,290 --> 00:28:07,430
